{"id": "1417792099675279361", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅，今日发布～欢迎大家收听、下载及分享～如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅**\n画家已寻觅到那恐怖的艺术，他掀开绘布，在投身前，邀友人赴一场色彩爆炸的癫狂奇旅。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: Pickman EP \"A Painter's Mad Adventure\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Pickman EP · A Painter's Mad Adventure**\nThe painter had finally found his terrifying art. He pulled back the canvas, and before he dove in, invited a friend on a wild journey with a chaotic explosion of color.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:39:37.866000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🌕", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792100258414642", "filename": "OST-250827-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 4734254, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792100258414642/OST-250827-.jpg?ex=69ccd9ca&is=69cb884a&hm=71509b2f505a09b5cf81f9e480c73070571fbd3f715b71ab6970f5e97439113e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1417792298506387466", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.不相似的朋友-Unalike Friends-**\n\n一次突然的造访，一次体贴的造访，一次幸福的造访。\n是相似的朋友，是不相似的朋友。\n哦，朋友，朋友，每个人都需要朋友。我要用什么来招待你，我的朋友？\n\nA sudden visit, a considerate visit, a joyous visit.\nThey are alike, yet unalike, friends.\nOh, friend, friend! Everyone needs a friend. What can I offer you, my dear friend?", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:40:25.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792297029865572", "filename": "1Unalike_Friends.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2240729, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792297029865572/1Unalike_Friends.jpg?ex=69ccd9f8&is=69cb8878&hm=4cf881fc713a059eb3ca2ebc1ac144280def1db4a6695ce7ab47f8a015dde1ce&"}, {"id": "1417792297579450450", "filename": "1.-Unalike_Friends-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19355712, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792297579450450/1.-Unalike_Friends-.wav?ex=69ccd9f9&is=69cb8879&hm=6e825de4d1b2f84b86cc577a67c02d1472ff0c510dda0db6ebc0d8a896fe5839&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1417792408338567269", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.步入迷乱-Descent into Delirium-**\n\n这是真实，这是狂魇，这是暗面，这是梦境。\n疯子和天才交替着喃喃低语，细些，再细些——不要挪开你的眼睛。\n\nThis is reality, this is a nightmare, this is the shadow side, this is a dream.\nThe madman and the genius whisper in turn. Lean in, closer—don't look away.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:40:51.457000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792407386193980", "filename": "2.-Descent_into_Delirium-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 15403992, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792407386193980/2.-Descent_into_Delirium-.wav?ex=69ccda13&is=69cb8893&hm=c3202eb3852e907e1ce07b6ecda37e5ee14214132903da053cd871b82287de28&"}, {"id": "1417792408036573214", "filename": "2Descent_into_Delirium.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2232255, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792408036573214/2Descent_into_Delirium.jpg?ex=69ccda13&is=69cb8893&hm=93734747bee5361e6286725651840a23209335f7ca3a5d27388f0dae0ef515e8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1417792565889073193", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.前沿艺术-Frontier Art-**\n\n诡谲将艺术家的灵感饲育，生长，生长，画师用色彩将真实解构，癫和痴在凌乱线条中生长。\n\nThe bizarre feeds the artist’s inspiration, growing and growing. The painter uses color to deconstruct reality; madness and obsession bloom in the chaotic lines.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:41:29.020000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792564941295717", "filename": "3Frontier_Art.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2228193, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792564941295717/3Frontier_Art.jpg?ex=69ccda38&is=69cb88b8&hm=db3591bf78a336173e34752f4f046924a2ca2404b09a303ae573bc6f16f005bf&"}, {"id": "1417792565540814969", "filename": "3.-Frontier_Art-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 14906114, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792565540814969/3.-Frontier_Art-.wav?ex=69ccda38&is=69cb88b8&hm=0bf73f79b1b5f359c482047a380150622e452e99efcb2c3bfe16339193cdd1b3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1417792683744952441", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.欢迎你！埃弗！-Welcome, Avery!-**\n\n吃啊，埃弗！看啊，埃弗！\n疯狂和真实之间，由色彩与艺术架构出的桥梁！\n只有我们两个在这里，只有我们能见到真相！\n\nEat, Avery! Look, Avery!\nA bridge between madness and reality, built from color and art!\nOnly we are here. Only we can see the truth!", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:41:57.119000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792682503438346", "filename": "4.-Welcome_Avery-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 24374216, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792682503438346/4.-Welcome_Avery-.wav?ex=69ccda54&is=69cb88d4&hm=679bf9dd65580c42573f25a06787f03ac09ffec4c4e4a97e30a4ff2f380d6d58&"}, {"id": "1417792683279257610", "filename": "4Welcome_Avery.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2240819, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792683279257610/4Welcome_Avery.jpg?ex=69ccda55&is=69cb88d5&hm=134ab8d3b2d8e0359eac826e780edb3cdf06f731d1b8e21f20d97143b83534f8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1417792891769585694", "channel_id": "1417792099675279361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.往彼处去-To the Other Side-**\n\n他已决意抛下此端，往彼端去。\n与他告别，但不要将祂遗忘。\n祂会提醒你，祂会注视你，那狂悖的疯子、天才的画师，和夜空中高悬的月亮。\n\nHe has decided to abandon this place and go to the other side.\nSay goodbye to him, but do not forget Him.\nHe will remind you, He will watch you: that madman, that genius painter, and the moon hanging high in the night sky.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T08:42:46.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417792890368823347", "filename": "5To_the_Other_Side.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2231587, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792890368823347/5To_the_Other_Side.jpg?ex=69ccda86&is=69cb8906&hm=f677c7dde9fbed78b74c2c8218d7915e371390f4bd8508aefc135d433383ed54&"}, {"id": "1417792890863747092", "filename": "5.-To_the_Other_Side-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 48602218, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417792099675279361/1417792890863747092/5.-To_the_Other_Side-.wav?ex=69ccda86&is=69cb8906&hm=977ce017d5957f707e47176cc702890e39466c4055fdd5788a34a5b207fea702&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417792099675279361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：皮克曼EP·疯画奇旅", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
